{"tid":13901,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"土炮海虎12\"Figure，點睇？","createTime":"2016-11-30T09:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T13:06:54.000Z","uid":2415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ea955905b96bfd9a9ec7a8f8a1536a132fbf7d","tid":13901,"uid":2415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"等咗咁耐終於有公司肯他媽的出可動海虎Figure！<br />\n好感動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實土炮公司肯出本地漫畫角色真係好有heart好有愛，<br />\n大公司出國際知名角色就話有銷量保證，<br />\n呢啲本土嘢真係專出俾香港人玩，要支持吓。<br />\n<br />\n之前ACG Toys有出龍虎門同古惑仔，<br />\nHottoys就出過步驚雲，不過個人好唔滿意，<br />\n樣唔似之餘手臂又肥過豬，仲要聶風走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻海虎戴眼鏡look都幾型，body可動性望落應該都唔差，有興趣可以去望吓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/deviltoys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdeviltoys&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=dc9dc6f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/deviltoys</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/170721_f384084501d0c8de8276b703c86cf813.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F170721_f384084501d0c8de8276b703c86cf813.jpg&h=7a75d93f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/170924_24f5fe7055ea138704db5fe18f097c32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F170924_24f5fe7055ea138704db5fe18f097c32.jpg&h=51f39fcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"293f1b5fc1c36691fdc98196207b012517f91098","tid":13901,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:20:14.000Z","msg":"睇左辦先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\